(learn more about query types) https://api.datamarket.azure.com/TeraDiscoveries/PDB_Access_1/v1/ Service root URL Sample Images Details Publisher Offer Terms The RCSB Protein Data Bank (http://www.rcsb.org) is the single worldwide repository of information about the 3D structures of large biological molecules. This offering places this information on Windows Azure to be used in bioinformatics. Included is information about the macromolecules’ atomic structure, bond characteristics, residues and crystallography. This offering also contains information on the published work that describes how this data was obtained.
